<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1280 gunēṁṭi māgha śukla dvitīyayu maṁga
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷavāramunāṁḍu śrīsiṁhagiri narasiṁhabhāratiśrīpādālu Upārjjiṁcina
<lb n="3"/>Ī maṭhānaku śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni nagaraṁ gala vṛttitōṁṭa kaśimikōṭakṣētrama O
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḍḍādikṣētrālu Iṭamīṁda vīru Ēmi vṛtti saṁpādiṁcinā vīri śiṣyapraśiṣya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vargamu Ī maṭhamu pratipāliṁci bhōgamu cēyaṁgalāru tāmunnu Upā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rjjiṁpaṁgalāru Ī vrittulu Ēminni krayāvikrayamabha yaṁbaḍayaru
<lb n="7"/>Ādhivaṭṭaṁbaḍayaru Ī dharmmu Adiṣṭāna śrīvaiṣṇavula rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> padineṇvi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṣayamu rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatṛṇāpi kṛtō dharma<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> pālanīyō manīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatṛrēva hi
<lb n="9"/>śatṛ<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> syāddharmmaśśatṛrna kasyacit <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrī śrī śrī 
</p>

